Text.val: It's possible that there's only a transfer_in_securities of the fraction fund present, instead of both fraction fund and the
fund to receive. For instance when the position in the original fund converted to less than 1 of the fund to receive.
The position in the fraction fund must then be liquidated and not added to the register.

SQL_STMT_U.val:
SELECT trans.tr_volgnummer FROM ( SELECT to_number(tr1.tr_volgnummer) "TR_VOLGNUMMER" FROM ( SELECT re_id "RE_ID" FROM producten_per_relatie pr INNER JOIN rekeningen_per_product rp ON rp.rpp_relatienummer = pr.ppr_relatienummer AND rp.rpp_productnummer = pr.ppr_productnummer AND rp.rpp_volgnr_per_product = pr.ppr_volgnr_per_product INNER JOIN rekeningen re ON re.re_nummer = rp.rpp_relatienummer AND re.re_rekening = rp.rpp_rekening_nummer AND re.re_soort = rp.rpp_rekeningsoort AND re.re_muntsoort = rp.rpp_valuta AND re.re_soort BETWEEN 100 AND 999 WHERE pr.ppr_id = ~1 ) product, ( SELECT TRIM(d.epp_id) "TR_VOLGNUMMER", ai.trai_tr_re_id "ACCOUNT_ID" FROM documents_links l INNER JOIN documents d ON d.id = l.document_id AND d.type = ( SELECT t.id FROM document_types t WHERE t.code = 'TRANS' ) INNER JOIN tap_tr_rel_account_info ai ON ai.trai_tr_volgnummer = to_number(TRIM(d.epp_id)) INNER JOIN documents d2 ON d2.id = l.source_document_id INNER JOIN document_types t2 ON t2.id = d2.type WHERE t2.code = 'CAPC_ID' AND TRIM(d2.epp_id) = ~2 ) tr1 WHERE tr1.account_id = product.re_id AND tr1.tr_volgnummer <> ~3 ) tr2 INNER JOIN transactions trans ON trans.tr_volgnummer = tr2.tr_volgnummer LEFT OUTER JOIN tap_bps_register bpr on bpr.bpsr_tr_volgnummer = tr2.tr_volgnummer and bpr.bpsr_ppr_id=~1
WHERE --When we are processing a transfer out, the corresponding transfer in must be of the fund to be received. Not a potential fraction fund! --In case we are processing a transfer in there can only be one corresponsing transfer out, so no need to range on the fund. (~9=0 or (trans.tr_symbool=~5 and trans.tr_optietype=~6 and trans.tr_exerciseprijs=~7 and trans.tr_expiratiedatum=~8))and ((~4=0 AND trans.tr_mut_gemaakt <> 'S') OR (~4=1 AND bpr.bpsr_tr_volgnummer IS NOT NULL))

SELECT SUM(rh.ryfh_free_to_sell_qty) "TOTAL_FREE_TO_SELL", COUNT(*) "NUMBER_OF_RECORDS" FROM tap_reynders_fifo_admin_header rh INNER JOIN tap_bps_register br ON br.bpsr_id = rh.ryfh_bpsr_id WHERE br.bpsr_ppr_id = ~1 AND br.bpsr_be_volgnummer = ~2 AND rh.ryfh_free_to_sell_qty > 0
